title: '125hz polling rate'
body: It does not have 1000hz polling rate. I downloaded their utility software and I tried to find a way to make this mouse redeemable but there's just no way to increase its polling rate. It's your basic 125hz mouse which is falsely being advertised on antesports' website as something which supports 1000hz polling rate and that is not true. If you really want a mouse which has 125hz polling and some rgb then you can easily find such mice for almost half the price. Otherwise the build quality is decent and feels decent.
